| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0489 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1bfd9f17-bf7e-52a1-9a92-42e3a22ace22"
